Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.63,0:00:05.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥準備
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.72,0:00:06.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥準備！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.50,0:00:08.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.65,0:00:09.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對手的眼睛很好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.23,0:00:11.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在把他們引至一擊必殺范圍內之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.74,0:00:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能讓他們發現我們的武裝
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.07,0:00:14.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可能只有那麼小一艘船
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.08,0:00:16.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東條 其餘的敵人呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.72,0:00:19.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敵1的後方三公里
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.10,0:00:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以每小時200公里速度接近的敵2 一分鐘就到
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.08,0:00:25.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡的海賊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.13,0:00:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,挑錯對手算你們倒霉！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.14,0:00:29.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停船！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:30.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停船就不殺！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.10,0:00:33.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰要停啊 笨蛋！

