Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.95,0:03:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼貨船會發動攻擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.35,0:03:28.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,司令艇炸飛了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.00,0:03:29.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快..快避開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.40,0:03:31.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左舷瞄準這裡了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.95,0:03:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是RPG！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.84,0:03:55.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不給力了 小毛賊們！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.93,0:04:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給它最後一下吧 雷姆
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.07,0:04:01.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.12,0:04:19.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明是我救的他
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.06,0:04:23.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我卻被打了 所以..
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.30,0:04:38.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會游泳嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.03,0:04:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,離陸地沒多少距離
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.06,0:04:43.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跳下去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.10,0:04:50.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好歹給你個救生圈 走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.53,0:04:56.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蔻蔻對海賊的毫不留情真是值得一筆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.29,0:04:58.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳在說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:03.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的我可是超級溫柔的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.63,0:05:08.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好了 差不多該到達南非了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.58,0:05:13.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非洲..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.09,0:05:27.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個是高希霸還是中國產？
